{"tid":1262244,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「青島啤酒」相關新聞兩則，連登仔注重健康飲食","createTime":"2019-06-27T15:13:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T16:30:02.000Z","uid":270500,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e92c6219f74e6a27cf4c51b0c232a0eedc5df1cc","tid":1262244,"uid":270500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T15:13:12.000Z","msg":"香港民眾透過網路發起眾籌，要在多國主流媒體頭版上刊登公開信，並促使各國能在G20會議上提出香港修訂逃犯條例相關討論。不過據香港網友爆料，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">南韓《中央日報》原本已確定會刊登公開信，但中國國企青島啤酒用「卑鄙手段」，以10倍以上「天價」奪去頭版版面</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2835935\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2835935&d=CAukz3ZnfWt5Iztj8dmWPC9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=6e72060a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2835935&h=368364fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2835935</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">多款啤酒驗出含除草劑致癌物 青島殘留物最多<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2281602/%E5%A4%9A%E6%AC%BE%E5%95%A4%E9%85%92%E9%A9%97%E5%87%BA%E5%90%AB%E9%99%A4%E8%8D%89%E5%8A%91%E8%87%B4%E7%99%8C%E7%89%A9%20%E9%9D%92%E5%B3%B6%E6%AE%98%E7%95%99%E7%89%A9%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%9A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2281602%2F%25E5%25A4%259A%25E6%25AC%25BE%25E5%2595%25A4%25E9%2585%2592%25E9%25A9%25